# Commander Pairing Reference

Last verified: 2026-07-23

## Sources of truth

- Rules: Wizards of the Coast, *Magic: The Gathering Comprehensive Rules*, rules 702.124 and 903.
- Card roster and current Oracle text: Scryfall card search / Oracle Cards bulk data.
- Runtime card spawning: `api.mtginfo.org`, whose query parser supports normal Scryfall terms but not Scryfall regular expressions.

The Lua chooser uses the online card roster to remain current, then independently validates every selected card against the rules below. This is safer than maintaining a static name list as the only authority.

